data.description: Cozy maintained ranch nestled on an expansive 0.69-acre lot, located in Salem Township. This charming two-bedroom, two-bathroom home boasts an enduring all-brick exterior and features recently updated flooring throughout. The spacious living room provides a welcoming atmosphere with loads of natural light & is complemented by an inviting eat-in kitchen equipped with all appliances. With a generously sized basement offering abundant storage & the potential for additional living space, this residence caters to both practicality & customization. The home is distinctly separate from the nearby development or plan, ensuring a sense of privacy with the flat & wooded backyard.  Convenience meets comfort in this property, conveniently located near major routes for easy commuting.  Seize the opportunity to call this charming ranch in Salem Township your own!
